</spec>
<atten4>
<ptxt>The coolant temperature is less than 95°C (203°F).</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>Check that the fan operates when the engine coolant temperature sensor connector is disconnected.</ptxt>
