</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>After the engine is warmed up, check that the fan operates as shown in the illustration on the left.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A139339E02" width="2.775699831in" height="3.779676365in"/>
</figure>
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>The coolant temperature at which the fan starts operating is approximately 95°C (203°F).</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>This system can also be checked using the intelligent tester.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Select the following menu items: Power train / Engine / Data List / Initial Engine Coolant Temp.</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
</s2>
